{"tid":1241833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［重整旗鼓］我地要嘅係撤回！唔係暫緩！唔好玩文字遊戲！","createTime":"2019-06-19T00:22:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T04:35:29.000Z","uid":216800,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"684214913b850cef8a1a6eca7ff65d75bad3d42d","tid":1241833,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:22:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無錯！</span></span>依一兩日大家的確鬆懈咗<br />\n你地唔係比林鄭眼淚感動咗呀？<br />\n你地你咪覺得件事真係到尾聲呀？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果唔係！</span></span><br />\n請好好地重拾當初出黎遊行嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">憤怒</span>情緒！<br />\n唔好忘記林鄭係有唔止一次出口術前科！<br />\n佢所有講嘅野！<br />\n一日未有撤回修定！佢所講嘅野一日都係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">廢話</span></span><br />\n我地一日都要反佢艇！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">落唔落台唔重要！</span></span><br />\n因為下一個被選中嘅狗都會繼承中共嘅意志！<br />\n<br />\n在撤回修定大前題下！<br />\n唔好浪費咁多位<span style=\"color: gold;\">義士</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">烈士</span>嘅<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">犧牲</span></span>、汗！同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">血</span></span>！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大</span><span style=\"color: green;\">家</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">勿</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">忘</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">初</span><span style=\"color: pink;\">心</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPa : 雖然我都有份開膠po，但 係我立場黎講，大家唞一唞氣 笑一笑 放鬆一下都係重要嘅元素。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但千祈唔好太鬆懈！</span></span>"},{"pid":"aa7e9cdf75f1f26abae31ef4334ce72bffce137c","tid":1241833,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T00:23:49.000Z","msg":"請大家努力推上熱門 長期警戒大家！"},{"pi